text: you so hv ban pol tha ao mcheasa robsakhnhom. montir khoumkheang cheatisrleanh robsakhnhom cheang avei del puok neang ban luonglom khnhom aoytow rk vea( ampeutouchcharit) . brasenbae trong min b nhchie sa ubayokl robsa puok neang ampikhnhom te noh khnhom nung thleaktowknong pheap vukavr robsa puok neang haey khnhom nung sthetnow knongchamnaom anak del lngongkhlaw cheaminkhan
